## 2. 전체 시스템 아키텍처

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  ThreadSafeVectorQueue<T>                    │
│                                                             │
│  Producer Thread 1 ──┐                                      │
│  Producer Thread 2 ──┼──► enqueue() ──► Vector<T> (내부)   │
│  Producer Thread N ──┘         ↑              ↓             │
│                          synchronized    synchronized        │
│  Consumer Thread 1 ──┐         ↓              ↑             │
│  Consumer Thread 2 ──┼──► dequeue() ◄── Vector<T> (내부)   │
│  Consumer Thread N ──┘                                      │
│                                                             │
│  Monitor: Object-level intrinsic lock (this)                │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

